%% Diagram: ISR cache lifecycle
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Built: build prerender
    Built --> Fresh: deploy to CDN
    Fresh --> Fresh: hit within\nrevalidate window
    Fresh --> Stale: window expires
    Stale --> Regenerating: first request\nafter expiry
    Regenerating --> Fresh: new HTML\nreplaces cache
    Regenerating --> Stale: regen error\n(retry next request)

    Fresh --> Regenerating: revalidatePath /\nrevalidateTag
    note right of Stale
        Caller still gets a fast
        cached response while a
        background re-render runs.
    end note
